                <h1 class="display-6">Menu Management Panel</h1><br/>
                 <p>This control center can be used to view/edit/delete menu items from a menu or add a new menu.</p>
                 <a href="#menu-toggle" class="btn btn-danger" id="menu-toggle">Toggle Menu</a>
            </div>
